msgctxt "428_Ochiai"
msgid "I did it! I'm a champion now!"
msgstr "¡Lo hice! ¡Ahora soy un campeón!"

msgctxt "440_Sodachi"
msgid "Great job, Fukushi. But remember, this is all thanks to Saejima-san!"
msgstr "Buen trabajo, Fukushi. Pero recuerda, ¡todo esto es gracias a Saejima-san!"

msgctxt "452_Ochiai"
msgid "Huh? Who do you think you're fooling? I won because I'm a fuckin' genius, that's why."
msgstr "¿Huh? ¿A quién intentas engañar? He ganado porque soy un puto genio, esa es la razón."

msgctxt "464_Ochiai"
msgid "I bet the word \"wunderkind\" was made for people like me."
msgstr "Apuesto a que la palabra \"niño prodigio\" se inventó para gente como yo."

msgctxt "476_Sodachi"
msgid "Ugh, he's beginning to piss me off..."
msgstr "Uf, está empezando a molestarme..."

msgctxt "488_Ochiai"
msgid "Heheh. Actually, I am a little grateful."
msgstr "Jejeje. En realidad, estoy un poco agradecido."

msgctxt "500_Sodachi"
msgid "What!? Really!? Oh, stop! You're making me blush!"
msgstr "¿¡Qué!? ¿¡En serio!? ¡Oh, para! ¡Me estás haciendo sonrojar!"

msgctxt "512_Ochiai"
msgid "No, not you, you idiot. The old man."
msgstr "No, tú no, idiota. El viejo."

msgctxt "524_Ochiai"
msgid "You weren't bad as a teacher. Thanks for everything. It was fun training with you."
msgstr "No has sido mal profesor. Gracias por todo. Ha sido divertido entrenar contigo."

msgctxt "536_Saejima"
msgid "Heh... Honestly, you were a pain in the ass to teach, but it was a learnin' experience."
msgstr "Je... La verdad, es que has sido un dolor en el culo enseñarte, pero ha sido una experiencia."

msgctxt "548_Ochiai"
msgid "Heheheh. Well, since I'm a champion now, I think I'll go ahead and celebrate with a nice long nap."
msgstr "Jejeje. Bueno, ya que soy campeón ahora, creo que voy a celebrarlo con una buena y larga siesta."

msgctxt "560_Sodachi"
msgid "Huh? You're going to sleep again!?"
msgstr "¿Uh? ¿¡Vas a dormir otra vez!?"

msgctxt "572_Ochiai"
msgid "You know I am! I'm tired! Responsible people have to know how to switch between work and rest."
msgstr "¡Sabes que sí! ¡Estoy cansado! La gente respinsable debe saber como cambiar entre trabajo y descanso."

msgctxt "584_Ochiai"
msgid "Well, I'm going to sleep. Just wake me up if anything important comes up."
msgstr "Bueno, voy a dormir. Despiertame si pasa algo importante."

msgctxt "596_Ochiai"
msgid "I hate it when people interrupt my sleep. But I guess I owe you, old man, so I'll wake up. And now we are even."
msgstr "Odio cuando la gente interrumpe mi sueño. Pero supongo que te debo una, viejo, así que me levantaré. Ahora estamos en paz."

msgctxt "608_Ochiai"
msgid "Good night!"
msgstr "¡Buenas noches!"

msgctxt "680_Sodachi"
msgid "What a handful..."
msgstr "Qué puñado..."

msgctxt "692_Saejima"
msgid "Yeah, but he did succeed in becomin' a champion. Ya gotta admit, that's impressive."
msgstr "Sí, pero ha conseguido convertirse en campeón. Debes admitirlo, eso es impresionante."

msgctxt "704_Sodachi"
msgid "I suppose so. Plus he's our third champion. Let's keep up the good work, Saejima-san!"
msgstr "Supongo. Además es nuestro tercer campeón. ¡Sigamos con el trabajo duro, Saejima-san!"

msgctxt "776_Ochiai"
msgid "The dojo's rank has increased."
msgstr "El rango del dojo fue aumentado."

msgctxt "860_Sodachi"
msgid "Congratulations!"
msgstr "¡Felicidades!"

msgctxt "872_Saejima"
msgid "Hm? For what?"
msgstr "¿Hm? ¿Para qué?"

msgctxt "884_Sodachi"
msgid "It appears that our friend Ehama-san got a new job! Isn't that great?"
msgstr "¡Parece que nuestro amigo Ehama-san consiguió un nuevo trabajo! ¿No es genial?"

msgctxt "896_Ehama"
msgid "It's all thanks to you. For the first time I was able to write something in the \"skills\" part of my resume: fighting!"
msgstr "Es todo gracias a tí. Por primera vez pude escribir algo en la sección de \"habilidades\" de mi currículum: ¡Luchar!"

msgctxt "908_Saejima"
msgid "That's great, Ehama. So what kind o' company you workin' at?"
msgstr "Eso es genial, Ehama. Entonces, ¿en qué tipo de compañía trabajas?"

msgctxt "920_Ehama"
msgid "It's a construction company. They mainly work on renovations for buildings and other facilities."
msgstr "Es una compañía de construcción. Principalmente trabajan en renovaciones para edificios y otras instalaciones."

msgctxt "932_Sodachi"
msgid "Renovations, huh? That's great! I was thinking about renovating our dojo, actually... Maybe I could ask you for help!"
msgstr "Renovaciones, ¿eh? ¡Eso es genial! Estaba pensando en renovar nuestro dojo, de hecho... ¡Quizá podría pedirte ayuda!"

msgctxt "944_Ehama"
msgid "Really!? That'd be great! If you let me help, I could get you the employee discount!"
msgstr "¿¡En serio!? ¡Eso sería genial! Si me dejas ayudar, ¡podría darte el descuento de empleado!"

msgctxt "956_Ehama"
msgid "Let's see... It would be around 1.5 million yen."
msgstr "Veamos... Sería alededor de 1.5 millones de yenes."

msgctxt "968_Sodachi"
msgid "Renovating will allow us to expand for higher level training facilities. Saejima-san! Come on! What do you say!?"
msgstr "Una renovación nos ayudaría a expandirnos a unas instalaciones de entrenamiento de más nivel. ¡Saejima-san! ¡Vamos! ¿¡Qué dices!?"

msgctxt "992_Saejima"
msgid "That ain't a bad idea. The timing's good, too. Let's do it."
msgstr "No es una mala idea. El momento es bueno. Hagámoslo."

msgctxt "1004_Sodachi"
msgid "Yippeeee! Thank you, Sae-chan! You're a doll!"
msgstr "¡Yippeeee! ¡Gracias Sae-chan! ¡Eres un amor!"

msgctxt "1016_Saejima"
msgid "......"
msgstr "......"

msgctxt "1028_Ehama"
msgid "Okay then! I'll go ahead and make the arrangements!"
msgstr "¡Bien! ¡Seguiré con los arreglos del dojo! Con permiso."

msgctxt "1088_Sodachi"
msgid "This is amazing! I'm so glad that we renovated! Look at this, Saejima-san!"
msgstr "¡E-Esto es una locura! ¡Hermoso, increíble, nuevo! ¡Mira esto Sae-chan!"

msgctxt "1100_Saejima"
msgid "Looks good. Now we can add lots of new trainin' equipment."
msgstr "Increíble de verdad. Ahora podemos sumar más cosas al equipo de entrenamiento."

msgctxt "1112_Ochiai"
msgid "Your dojo renovation is complete. Each facility can now be upgraded to Level 3."
msgstr "La renovación del Dojo fue completada. Cada instalación se puede mejorar a nivel 3."

msgctxt "1124_Sodachi"
msgid "Hopefully this will attract a lot of new apprentices. Heheheh..."
msgstr "Esperemos que vengan a inscribirse más aprendices con esta mejora. Jejeje..."

msgctxt "1136_Saejima"
msgid "A renovation, huh? That'd be nice. But we ain't got that kind o' money."
msgstr "Una renovación, ¿eh? Eso estaría bien. Pero no tenemos ese dinero."

msgctxt "1148_Sodachi"
msgid "Aw..."
msgstr "Aw..."

msgctxt "1160_Ehama"
msgid "That's too bad... But, no worries. I can do it anytime, so just let me know when you're ready."
msgstr "Que mal... Pero, no te preocupes. Puedo hacerlo cuando sea, así que solo hazmelo saber cuando estés listo."

msgctxt "1172_Sodachi"
msgid "I guess we just have to save our money..."
msgstr "Parece que tenemos que ahorrar dinero..."

msgctxt "1184_Saejima"
msgid "This ain't the kind o' decision to make on a whim. We should pass this time."
msgstr "Esta no es una decisión que la tomes por capricho. Deberíamos pasar esta vez."

msgctxt "1196_Sodachi"
msgid "Aw..."
msgstr "Aw..."

msgctxt "1208_Ehama"
msgid "I understand. No need to rush. We can do it anytime, so just let me know if you change your mind."
msgstr "Entiendo. No hay prisa. Podemos hacerlo cuando gustes, así que avísame cuando cambies de opinión."

msgctxt "1220_Sodachi"
msgid "No fun! Boo! Cheapskate!"
msgstr "¡Aburridooo! ¡Booo! ¡Tacaño!"

msgctxt "1232_Saejima"
msgid "......"
msgstr "......"

msgctxt "1316_Sodachi"
msgid "The dojo's rank increased! Now more apprentices are sure to join, and the money will start flowing! Heheheh!"
msgstr "¡El rango del Dojo aumento! ¡Ahora se unirán más aprendices, y el dinero empezará a fluir! ¡Jejeje!"

msgctxt "1328_Saejima"
msgid "......"
msgstr "......"

msgctxt "1400_Sodachi"
msgid "The dojo's rank decreased! This is a nightmare... Ugh, my chest hurts... The stress is killing me! Saejima-san! Do something!"
msgstr "¡El rango del Dojo ha caído! E-Esto es una terrible... Ahg, me duele el pecho... ¡El estrés me mata! Saejima-san! ¡Haz algo, por favor!"

msgctxt "1412_Saejima"
msgid "(Will he pipe down already...)"
msgstr "(Espero que cierre el pico...)"

msgctxt "1484_Ochiai"
msgid "This can't be true... I lost!? <Italic>Me</Italic>!? The other guy must have cheated somehow... This is really starting to piss me off!"
msgstr "Esto no puede ser verdad... ¿¡He perdido!? ¿¡<Italic>Yo</Italic>!? El otro tipo debe haber hecho trampa de alguna forma... ¡Esto está empezando a molestarme!"

msgctxt "1496_Sodachi"
msgid "It's too bad about the loss. Seems like he's ticked off about it. He's starting to scare me a little bit..."
msgstr "Es una lástima la derrota. Parece que está molesto. Está empezando a asustarme un poco..."

msgctxt "1508_Sodachi"
msgid "But there's no use dwelling in the past. Let's keep up the good training so that we can turn this anger into a more positive strength!"
msgstr "Pero de nada sirve vivir en el pasado. ¡Sigamos entrenando así para que podamos convertir esa rabia en una fuerza más positiva!"

msgctxt "1592_Sodachi"
msgid "Great job! You totally annihilated your opponent! You really are a genius, Fukushi-sama! And now you're even stronger and more confident than before!"
msgstr "¡Buen trabajo! ¡Has aniquilado totalmente a tu oponente! ¡Eres un genio, Fukushi-sama! ¡Y ahora eres incluso mas fuerte y seguro de tí mismo que antes!"

msgctxt "1604_Ochiai"
msgid "Heheheh... It was nothing. I could've beaten the guy with my pinky!"
msgstr "Jejeje... No ha sido nada. ¡Podría haber derrotado al tipo con el meñique!"

msgctxt "1616_Sodachi"
msgid "Keep up the good work and get that money－ Uh, I mean those wins! Banzai Fukushi Ochiai!"
msgstr "Sigue trabajando así de bien y consigue ese dinero - Uhh, digo, ¡esas victorias! ¡Banzai Fukushi Ochiai!"

msgctxt "1712_Sodachi"
msgid "You will be competing in Dragon's Gate. This is a match for beginning fighters. The level of entry isn't high, so it's perfect for practice."
msgstr "Compitiendo en la Puerta del Dragón. Este es un combate para los combatientes principiantes. El nivel de entrada no es alto, así que es perfecto para practicar."

msgctxt "1724_Sodachi"
msgid "This is the beginning of all history. Go Sodachi Dojo!"
msgstr "Este es el comienzo de una gran historia. ¡Vamos Dojo de Sodachi!"

msgctxt "1736_Sodachi"
msgid "You will be competing in Brawlfest."
msgstr "Competirás en el Brawlfest."

msgctxt "1748_Sodachi"
msgid "Fighting connoisseurs! Go Sodachi Dojo!"
msgstr "¡Conocedores de la lucha! ¡Vamos Dojo Sodachi!"

msgctxt "1760_Sodachi"
msgid "You will be competing in the Regular Tryouts. This is a match held regularly at the Coliseum for mid-level fighters."
msgstr "Competirás en las eliminatorias regulares. Este combate se celebra regularmente en el coliseo para luchadores de nivel medio."

msgctxt "1772_Sodachi"
msgid "Well, time's a-wasting! Go Sodachi Dojo!"
msgstr "¡Bien! ¡Estamos desperdiciando tiempo! ¡Vamos Dojo Sodachi!"

msgctxt "1784_Sodachi"
msgid "You will be competing in Shuffle Zone. The skill levels of the fighters in this match are unknown."
msgstr "Competirás en Shuffle Zone. El nivel de habilidad de los luchadores aquí es desconocido..."

msgctxt "1796_Sodachi"
msgid "I hope your opponent isn't too strong... Wow, my heart is racing! Go Sodachi Dojo!"
msgstr "Espero que tu oponente no sea muy fuerte... ¡Ey! ¡Mi corazón está como loco! ¡Vamos Dojo Sodachi!"

msgctxt "1808_Sodachi"
msgid "You will be competing in the Big Money match. The prize purse for winning this match is incredible! Money! MONEY! Heheheh!"
msgstr "Competirás en la Gran Metalico. ¡La bolsa de premio por ganar este combate es inigualable! ¡Dinero! ¡DINERO! ¡JE, JE, JE!"

msgctxt "1820_Sodachi"
msgid "All right, let's go! Go Sodachi Dojo! Go get me that money!"
msgstr "¡Bien, en marcha! ¡Vamos Dojo Sodachi! ¡Ve a traerme ese dinero!"

msgctxt "1832_Sodachi"
msgid "You will be competing in Rising Stars. This is a famous event where young fighters with great potential gather to prove themselves. A true first step."
msgstr "Competirás en las Grandes Estrellas. Este gran evento es donde luchadores jóvenes con gran potencial prueban que son capaces. Una oportunidad única."

msgctxt "1844_Sodachi"
msgid "Well, time's a-wasting! Go Sodachi Dojo!"
msgstr "¡Bien! ¡Estamos desperdiciando tiempo! ¡Vamos Dojo Sodachi!"

msgctxt "1856_Sodachi"
msgid "You will be competing in the Sink or Swim match. This is an event for fighters who are just getting started. Let your skills speak for you."
msgstr "Competirás en la Alpozo o nada. Este evento es para luchadores que están empezando. Acá deja que tus habilidades fluyan."

msgctxt "1868_Sodachi"
msgid "Believe in your own abilities! Go Sodachi Dojo!"
msgstr "¡Cree en tus habilidades! ¡Vamos Dojo Sodachi!"

msgctxt "1880_Sodachi"
msgid "You will be competing in the Winner's Circle. This is an event for undefeated fighters. Be ready for some strong competition."
msgstr "Competirás en el Círculo de ganadores. Este evento es para luchadores invictos. Prepárate para unas peleas de las complicadas."

msgctxt "1892_Sodachi"
msgid "You won't be able to compete again if you lose, so make sure to win! Go Sodachi Dojo!"
msgstr "No podrás competir de nuevo si pierdes. ¡Así que asegurarte de ganar! ¡Vamos Dojo Sodachi!"

msgctxt "1904_Sodachi"
msgid "You will be competing in the Veteran's Showdown. This is an event for fighters with a long training history."
msgstr "Competirás en el Show para Veteranos. Este evento reúne a luchadores con una historia en el coliseo."

msgctxt "1916_Sodachi"
msgid "It's time to put what you've learned to the test and show 'em who we are! Go Sodachi Dojo!"
msgstr "¡Es hora de poner a lo aprendido y destrales de que estás hecho! ¡Vamos Dojo Sodachi!"

msgctxt "1928_Sodachi"
msgid "You will be competing in the Coliseum Opening Fight.\\r\n"\n"It's an extremely high-profile match that is, you guessed it, the opening event at the Coliseum!"
msgstr "Competirás en la Pelea de Apertura del Coliseo.\\r\n"\n"¡Son combates con luchadores de un nivel alto que se realiza como evento de apertura del Coliseo!"

msgctxt "1940_Sodachi"
msgid "This kind of attention-grabbing fight attracts some pretty strong fighters, but that's no reason for you to lose! Go Sodachi Dojo!"
msgstr "Este tipo de combates llama mucho la atención a luchadores bastante fuertes, ¡pero esa no es razón alguna para perder! ¡Vamos Dojo Sodachi!"

msgctxt "1952_Sodachi"
msgid "You will be competing in King of the Mountain. This is a very high-level match for skilled fighters who have what it takes to be champion."
msgstr "Competirás en El Rey de la Montaña. Trata de un combate de alto nivel para luchadores que tienen sangre para ser campeón."

msgctxt "1964_Sodachi"
msgid "Brush up your own skills by fighting stronger opponents. Go Sodachi Dojo!"
msgstr "Demuestra y arrasa contra luchadores más fuertes. ¡Vamos Dojo Sodachi!"

msgctxt "1976_Sodachi"
msgid "You will be competing in Power Masters."
msgstr "Competirás en los Maestros del Poder."

msgctxt "1988_Sodachi"
msgid "Fighters proud of their power gather at this event, so the fights are sure to be intense. Give it your all, super Sodachi Dojo!"
msgstr "Son luchadores orgullosos de su poder y gran habilidad, por lo que las peleas no serán nada fáciles. ¡Así que ve por todo! ¡Vamos Dojo Sodachi!"

msgctxt "2000_Sodachi"
msgid "You will be competing in Speed Masters."
msgstr "Competirás en los Maestros de la Velocidad."

msgctxt "2012_Sodachi"
msgid "Fighters proud of their level of speed gather at this event. You're perfect for this one! Go Sodachi Dojo!"
msgstr "Son luchadores destacados por su gran velocidad. ¡Este evento es perfecto para ti! ¡Vamos Dojo Sodachi!"

msgctxt "2024_Sodachi"
msgid "You will be competing in Technique Masters. This event is only for fighters above a certain technique level."
msgstr "Competirás en Maestros de la Técnica. Este evento es solo para luchadores que superan un cierto nivel de técnica."

msgctxt "2036_Sodachi"
msgid "Only fighters with superior technique fight in this event, so stay focused! Go Sodachi Dojo!"
msgstr "¡Solo luchadores con un nivel técnico alto pasan a este evento! ¡Concéntrate! ¡Vamos Dojo Sodachi!"

msgctxt "2048_Sodachi"
msgid "You will be competing in Rookie Stars. As the name suggests, this is a match for rookie fighters aiming to be number one."
msgstr "You will be competing in Rookie Stars. As the name suggests, this is a match for rookie fighters aiming to be number one."

msgctxt "2060_Sodachi"
msgid "This is the highest level match, so make sure you're ready. Go Sodachi Dojo, the strongest dojo in Kamurocho!"
msgstr "Este es un combate de altísimo nivel, asegúrate de estar preparado. ¡Vamos Dojo Sodachi! ¡El Dojo más fuerte de Kamurocho!"

msgctxt "2084_Ochiai"
msgid "This can't be true... I lost!? <Italic>Me</Italic>!? The other guy must have cheated somehow... This is really starting to piss me off!"
msgstr "Esto no puede ser verdad... ¿¡He perdido!? ¿¡<Italic>Yo</Italic>!? El otro tipo debe haber hecho trampa de alguna forma... ¡Esto está empezando a molestarme!"

msgctxt "2096_Sodachi"
msgid "It's too bad about the loss. Seems like he's ticked off about it. He's starting to scare me a little bit..."
msgstr "Es una lástima la derrota. Parece que está molesto. Está empezando a asustarme un poco..."

msgctxt "2108_Sodachi"
msgid "But there's no use dwelling in the past. Let's keep up the good training so that we can turn this anger into a more positive strength!"
msgstr "Pero de nada sirve vivir en el pasado. ¡Sigamos entrenando así para que podamos convertir esa rabia en una fuerza más positiva!"

msgctxt "2204_Sodachi"
msgid "Now it's time to participate in a tournament. We had our ups and downs, but you've become a pretty good fighter."
msgstr "Es hora de participar en un torneo. Hemos tenido nuestros altibajos, pero te has convertido en un luchado bastante bueno."

msgctxt "2216_Saejima"
msgid "He's right. Ya already got the potential, so just stay on yer guard and you'll be fine. Stay focused n' give it yer best shot."
msgstr "Tiene razón. Tienes el potencial, así que mantente en guardia y estarás bien. No pierdas la concentración y saca tu mejor versión."

msgctxt "2228_Ochiai"
msgid "I'm always on guard! It's not gonna take long for me to win. You'll see."
msgstr "¡Siempre estoy en guardia! No voy a tardar mucho en ganar. Ya lo verás."

msgctxt "2240_Sodachi"
msgid "We have high hopes for you, Fukushi. Go and get that win and bring back some money! Go Sodachi Dojo!"
msgstr "Tenemos altas esperanzas en tí, Fukushi. ¡Ve, consigue esa victoria y trae algo de dinero! ¡Vamos Sodachi Dojo!"

msgctxt "2276_Sodachi"
msgid "Wow, you really are an amazing fighter! I'm sure Fukushi-kun learned a lot, too."
msgstr "Wow, ¡realmente eres un luchador tremendo! Estoy seguro que Fukushi-kun ha aprendido mucho también."

msgctxt "2288_Ochiai"
msgid "You're the real deal... Well, I'll let you go for today."
msgstr "No eres poca cosa... Bueno, te dejaré ir por hoy."

msgctxt "2300_Saejima"
msgid "Heh... Just let me know when ya wanna go at it again."
msgstr "Je... Solo haze saber cuando quieras intentarlo otra vez."

msgctxt "2396_Sodachi"
msgid "Sparring or not, I can't believe he beat you! Looks like he's getting a lot stronger!"
msgstr "Sparring or not, I can't believe he beat you! Looks like he's getting a lot stronger!"

msgctxt "2408_Ochiai"
msgid "Yay! That was easy! I don't know if there's anything else for this old man to teach me!"
msgstr "¡Yey! ¡Eso fue fácil! ¡No sé si hay algo más que este viejo pueda enseñarme!"

msgctxt "2420_Sodachi"
msgid "Hmm... Looks like it's gone completely to his head. This isn't good..."
msgstr "Hmm... Parece que se le ha subido por completo a la cabeza. Esto no es bueno..."

msgctxt "2504_Sodachi"
msgid "It's time for some sparring. Show Fukushi-kun just how good you are, Saejima-san!"
msgstr "Es hora de entrenar un poco. ¡Enséñale a Fukushi-kun lo bueno que eres, Saejima-san!"

msgctxt "2516_Saejima"
msgid "Right. I'll teach 'im how it feels to fight a real fighter."
msgstr "Bien. Le enseñaré como se siente pelear con un luchador de verdad."

msgctxt "2528_Ochiai"
msgid "Whatever. Just don't come crying to me after I kick your ass. Let's do it!"
msgstr "Lo que sea. Solo te digo que no me vengas llorando cuando te patee el culo. ¡Hagámoslo!"

msgctxt "2552_Sodachi"
msgid "You want him to try solo training? I'm a bit reluctant to allow Fukushi-kun to lead his own training..."
msgstr "You want him to try solo training? I'm a bit reluctant to allow Fukushi-kun to lead his own training..."

msgctxt "2564_Saejima"
msgid "Let's give it a try. You can choose yer own trainin' routine. Just don't go slackin' off."
msgstr "Let's give it a try. You can choose yer own trainin' routine. Just don't go slackin' off."

msgctxt "2576_Ochiai"
msgid "Heheheh. We should have been doing this from the very beginning. Just relax and leave everything to me."
msgstr "Heheheh. We should have been doing this from the very beginning. Just relax and leave everything to me."

msgctxt "2588_Saejima"
msgid "......"
msgstr "......"

msgctxt "2648_Saejima"
msgid "How was it? Ya learn anythin'?"
msgstr "How was it? Ya learn anythin'?"

msgctxt "2660_Ochiai"
msgid "I worked crazy hard! I wish you could have seen me! In fact, I probably could have even gone a little easier on myself! Ha!"
msgstr "I worked crazy hard! I wish you could have seen me! In fact, I probably could have even gone a little easier on myself! Ha!"

msgctxt "2672_Saejima"
msgid "(Huh. Not bad.)"
msgstr "(Heh. No está mal.)"

msgctxt "2708_Saejima"
msgid "How was it? Ya learn anythin'?"
msgstr "How was it? Ya learn anythin'?"

msgctxt "2720_Ochiai"
msgid "It went okay. I worked hard and slacked off the perfect amount. It's important for people to practice moderation, right?"
msgstr "It went okay. I worked hard and slacked off the perfect amount. It's important for people to practice moderation, right?"

msgctxt "2732_Saejima"
msgid "(What's he doin' slacking off?)"
msgstr "(What's he doin' slacking off?)"

msgctxt "2780_Saejima"
msgid "How was it? Ya learn anythin'?"
msgstr "How was it? Ya learn anythin'?"

msgctxt "2792_Ochiai"
msgid "Zzz..."
msgstr "Zzz..."

msgctxt "2804_Saejima"
msgid "(What the hell...)"
msgstr "(What the hell...)"

msgctxt "2888_Saejima"
msgid "How's about we rest this time? Rest is important too."
msgstr "How's about we rest this time? Rest is important too."

msgctxt "2900_Sodachi"
msgid "Yay! That's a wonderful idea! Let's rest away!"
msgstr "Yay! That's a wonderful idea! Let's rest away!"

msgctxt "2984_Ochiai"
msgid "Zzz..."
msgstr "Zzz..."

msgctxt "2996_Sodachi"
msgid "*snores* Gaaaa... Gaaaa... *snores* Mmmm..."
msgstr "*snores* Gaaaa... Gaaaa... *snores* Mmmm..."

msgctxt "3032_Sodachi"
msgid "Googa googa... *snores* Nyaar... *snores*\\r\n"\n"Heheh, but I can't eat anymore... *snores*"
msgstr "Googa googa... *snores* Nyaar... *snores*\\r\n"\n"Heheh, but I can't eat anymore... *snores*"

msgctxt "3044_Saejima"
msgid "......"
msgstr "......"

msgctxt "3116_Sodachi"
msgid "Wow! I feel so refreshed! Resting really is necessary sometimes."
msgstr "Wow! I feel so refreshed! Resting really is necessary sometimes."

msgctxt "3200_Saejima"
msgid "All right. This time I'm gonna teach ya a potential Finishing Move."
msgstr "All right. This time I'm gonna teach ya a potential Finishing Move."

msgctxt "3212_Saejima"
msgid "(Which move should I teach 'im?)"
msgstr "(Which move should I teach 'im?)"

msgctxt "3248_Saejima"
msgid "Okay, let's get started."
msgstr "Okay, let's get started."

msgctxt "3260_Saejima"
msgid "Let's work on the move you ain't mastered yet. Okay, let's get started."
msgstr "Vamos a enfocarnos en el movimiento que aún no has dominado. Bien, empecemos."

msgctxt "3332_Saejima"
msgid "...So, that's it. Think ya got it?"
msgstr "...So, that's it. Think ya got it?"

msgctxt "3344_Ochiai"
msgid "Not really... I think I'm starting to get sleepy..."
msgstr "Not really... I think I'm starting to get sleepy..."

msgctxt "3356_Saejima"
msgid "(...He couldn't learn it after one try. But he'll get it next time.)"
msgstr "(...He couldn't learn it after one try. But he'll get it next time.)"

msgctxt "3440_Saejima"
msgid "I'm sure ya got it down now. Give it a try."
msgstr "I'm sure ya got it down now. Give it a try."

msgctxt "3452_Sodachi"
msgid "Softly please..."
msgstr "Softly please..."

msgctxt "3464_Sodachi"
msgid "Aaaaagh!"
msgstr "¡Aaaaagh!"

msgctxt "3488_Saejima"
msgid "Good! You did it just right that time. Now don't forget what ya learned."
msgstr "Good! You did it just right that time. Now don't forget what ya learned."

msgctxt "3512_Ochiai"
msgid "He learned <Color:9>Tiger Slam<Color:Default>."
msgstr "He learned <Color:9>Tiger Slam<Color:Default>."

msgctxt "3524_Ochiai"
msgid "He learned <Color:9>Tiger Suplex SP<Color:Default>."
msgstr "He learned <Color:9>Tiger Suplex SP<Color:Default>."

msgctxt "3536_Ochiai"
msgid "He learned <Color:9>Tiger Throw<Color:Default>."
msgstr "He learned <Color:9>Tiger Throw<Color:Default>."

msgctxt "3548_Ochiai"
msgid "He learned <Color:9>Tiger Flying Knee<Color:Default>."
msgstr "He learned <Color:9>Tiger Flying Knee<Color:Default>."

msgctxt "3560_Ochiai"
msgid "He learned <Color:9>Essence of Smashing<Color:Default>."
msgstr "He learned <Color:9>Essence of Smashing<Color:Default>."

msgctxt "3572_Ochiai"
msgid "He learned <Color:9>Essence of Face Crushing<Color:Default>."
msgstr "He learned <Color:9>Essence of Face Crushing<Color:Default>."

msgctxt "3584_Ochiai"
msgid "He learned <Color:9>Essence of Clotheslining<Color:Default>."
msgstr "He learned <Color:9>Essence of Clotheslining<Color:Default>."

msgctxt "3596_Ochiai"
msgid "He learned <Color:9>Essence of Fence Smashing<Color:Default>."
msgstr "He learned <Color:9>Essence of Fence Smashing<Color:Default>."

msgctxt "3608_Ochiai"
msgid "He learned <Color:9>Essence of Might<Color:Default>."
msgstr "He learned <Color:9>Essence of Might<Color:Default>."

msgctxt "3620_Ochiai"
msgid "He learned <Color:9>Tiger Crush<Color:Default>."
msgstr "He learned <Color:9>Tiger Crush<Color:Default>."

msgctxt "3704_Sodachi"
msgid "Welcome back. Did you guys have a good time? Things were fun here... by myself... *sniffle*"
msgstr "Welcome back. Did you guys have a good time? Things were fun here... by myself... *sniffle*"

msgctxt "3728_Sodachi"
msgid "All right, see you next time."
msgstr "All right, see you next time."

msgctxt "3788_Saejima"
msgid "How's about we call it quits for today n' go out for a drink?"
msgstr "How's about we call it quits for today n' go out for a drink?"

msgctxt "3800_Sodachi"
msgid "That sounds great! You have to know how to separate work and play, right? Wait..."
msgstr "That sounds great! You have to know how to separate work and play, right? Wait..."

msgctxt "3812_Saejima"
msgid "See ya later. Let's go, Fukushi."
msgstr "See ya later. Let's go, Fukushi."

msgctxt "3824_Sodachi"
msgid "Okay! Have a good time!"
msgstr "¡Que te vaya bien!"

msgctxt "3836_Sodachi"
msgid "Hmph..."
msgstr "Mmpf..."

msgctxt "3908_Sodachi"
msgid "Hmmm..."
msgstr "Mmmm..."

msgctxt "3920_Saejima"
msgid "Somethin' wrong?"
msgstr "Somethin' wrong?"

msgctxt "3932_Sodachi"
msgid "Nothing... It's just that Fukushi-kun seems to be really pissed off lately."
msgstr "Nothing... It's just that Fukushi-kun seems to be really pissed off lately."

msgctxt "3944_Saejima"
msgid "......"
msgstr "......"

msgctxt "3956_Sodachi"
msgid "We've been pushing him in training for so long; I'm afraid he's going to explode with frustration if he doesn't win a tournament soon."
msgstr "We've been pushing him in training for so long; I'm afraid he's going to explode with frustration if he doesn't win a tournament soon."

msgctxt "4028_Sodachi"
msgid "Fukushi-kun lost..."
msgstr "Fukushi-kun lost..."

msgctxt "4040_Saejima"
msgid "Yeah... Where is he right now?"
msgstr "Yeah... Where is he right now?"

msgctxt "4052_Sodachi"
msgid "Now that you mention it, he hasn't come back to the dojo at all. I guess the loss was a shock."
msgstr "Now that you mention it, he hasn't come back to the dojo at all. I guess the loss was a shock."

msgctxt "4064_Sodachi"
msgid "I'll go and look for him!"
msgstr "I'll go and look for him!"

msgctxt "4076_Saejima"
msgid "......"
msgstr "......"

msgctxt "4136_Sodachi"
msgid "*pant* Here he is!"
msgstr "*jadeo* ¡Aquí está!"

msgctxt "4148_Ochiai"
msgid "......"
msgstr "......"

msgctxt "4160_Saejima"
msgid "What happened?"
msgstr "¿Por qué?"

msgctxt "4172_Ochiai"
msgid "Hmph! Don't give me that crap! I did everything you said, and I couldn't win!"
msgstr "Hmph! Don't give me that crap! I did everything you said, and I couldn't win!"

msgctxt "4184_Ochiai"
msgid "Do you realize how long I've been training? Make me a champion already!"
msgstr "Do you realize how long I've been training? Make me a champion already!"

msgctxt "4196_Ochiai"
msgid "Hmph... This is just getting me depressed..."
msgstr "Hmph... This is just getting me depressed..."

msgctxt "4208_Saejima"
msgid "(I'm glad he's back, but it looks like he's lost a lot o' motivation. Better get him that champion belt. And quick...)"
msgstr "(Me alegra que haya vuelto, pero parece que ha perdido mucha motivación. Será mejor conseguirle ese cinturón de campeón. Y rápido...)."

msgctxt "4292_Sodachi"
msgid "Hey, Saejima-san! I was waiting for you! Shall we start our training now?"
msgstr "Hey, Saejima-san! I was waiting for you! Shall we start our training now?"

msgctxt "4304_Saejima"
msgid "Yeah, let's get started."
msgstr "Yeah, let's get started."

msgctxt "4316_Sodachi"
msgid "All right! Here's to another day of training! Let's get to work!"
msgstr "All right! Here's to another day of training! Let's get to work!"

msgctxt "4340_Saejima"
msgid "Maybe later."
msgstr "Maybe later."

msgctxt "4352_Sodachi"
msgid "Oh, that's too bad. But you are a pretty busy person. Come back when you have more time."
msgstr "Oh, that's too bad. But you are a pretty busy person. Come back when you have more time."

msgctxt "4364_Ochiai"
msgid "Renovate for 1.5 million yen"
msgstr "Renovate for 1.5 million yen"

msgctxt "4376_Ochiai"
msgid "Not Now"
msgstr "Ahora no"

msgctxt "4388_Ochiai"
msgid "Start Training"
msgstr "Start Training"

msgctxt "4400_Ochiai"
msgid "Not Now"
msgstr "Ahora no"

